companyProfile: {'companyDescription': "Britannia Industries Limited is an India-based food products company. The Company is primarily engaged in the manufacturing and sale of various food products. The Company's product categories include biscuits, dairy, breads, rusk, cakes, nutrition bar, and snacking. Its biscuit products include Good Day, Marie Gold, NutriChoice, Milk Bikis, Tiger, 50-50, Jim Jam, Treat, Little Hearts, Pure Magic, Nice Time and Biscafe. The Company's dairy products include cheese, Winkin' Cow, Come Alive Paneer, Come Alive Dahi, ghee and Dairy Whitener. Its bread products include gourmet breads, white bread and wheat flour breads. Its gourmet breads include Fruit Bun, fruit bread, Choco bread and Choco Bun. Its white breads include Healthy Slice Bread, Sweet Bread, Vitarich Bread and Sandwich Bread. Its cake products include Gobbles, Fudge, Muffils, Nuts and Raisin Romance Cake, Roll Yo! and Tiffin Fun.
